      "rationale": "SST k-ω turbulence model selected based on published FDA pump benchmark comparisons (Hariharan et al. 2011); realizable k-ε and LES evaluated as alternatives — SST k-ω showed lowest bias across all operating points. Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model used with Bludszuweit correction; model form uncertainty quantified within the UQ campaign. Achieved level 4."
